commit_message:
Pretty-print output during bootstrap process

This change makes reading the standard output a little easier. For
example:

        TASK [sshd : set_fact]
        ok: [localhost] => {"ansible_facts": {"sshd_packages": ["openssh-server", "openssh-sftp-server"]}, "changed": false}

becomes

        TASK [sshd : set_fact]
        ok: [localhost] => {
            "ansible_facts": {
                "sshd_packages": [
                    "openssh-server",
                    "openssh-sftp-server"
                ]
            },
            "changed": false
        }

The `unset` commands were sorted alphabetically to make reading the
scripts a little easier.

Change-Id: Ibf68a7cb253878ac5438e8b55d32b79fb8cbfbd5
